<header class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 4rem;">
  <span class="eyebrow">Analysis</span>
  <h1>SWOT &amp; Competitor Comparison</h1>
  <p>How TUI Airways stacks up against itself &mdash; strengths, weaknesses, opportunities, threats &mdash; and against its closest UK rivals.</p>
</header>

<main class="wrap">

  <div class="section-label">Comparative Analysis</div>
  <h2 class="title">Who are TUI's competitors?</h2>
  <div class="definition-box">
    TUI Airways is best compared to other UK leisure / short-haul carriers like <strong>Jet2.com</strong> (its closest direct rival in the package holiday space), <strong>easyJet</strong>, and <strong>Ryanair</strong> (pure low-cost). It differs from full-service carriers like <strong>British Airways</strong>.
  </div>

  <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:3rem;">Fleet &amp; Scale</div>
  <h2 class="title">Fleet size comparison (approx. 2025)</h2>
  <div class="bar-chart">
    <div class="bar-col"><div class="bar-val">~71</div><div class="bar" style="height:53%;"></div><div class="bar-label">TUI Airways</div></div>
    <div class="bar-col"><div class="bar-val">~135</div><div class="bar" style="height:100%;"></div><div class="bar-label">Jet2.com</div></div>
    <div class="bar-col"><div class="bar-val">Large</div><div class="bar" style="height:80%;"></div><div class="bar-label">easyJet (A320s)</div></div>
    <div class="bar-col"><div class="bar-val">#1 in Europe</div><div class="bar" style="height:95%;"></div><div class="bar-label">Ryanair</div></div>
  </div>
  <p class="lead">TUI Airways: ~71 aircraft, Boeing-focused (including B787 Dreamliners). Jet2.com: ~133&ndash;135 aircraft, larger and rapidly expanding. easyJet: large Airbus A320-family fleet. Ryanair: Europe's largest airline by passenger numbers.</p>

  <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:3rem;">Punctuality</div>
  <h2 class="title">On-time performance</h2>
  <div class="grid cols-3">
    <div class="card">
      <h3><span class="icon-badge">&#9203;</span> Criticism for delays</h3>
      <p>TUI has faced criticism for delays in recent years.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
